# Performance & Accessibility Guidelines - Liquid Glass Snowcap Portfolio

## Performance Targets
- Lighthouse Performance Score: ≥ 90
- Lighthouse Accessibility Score: ≥ 95
- Lighthouse Best Practices Score: ≥ 95
- First Contentful Paint: < 1.5s
- Largest Contentful Paint: < 2.5s
- Cumulative Layout Shift: < 0.1

## Animation Performance
- 60fps target for all animations
- Use `transform` and `opacity` only
- Throttle to `requestAnimationFrame`
- Avoid layout-triggering properties
- Use `will-change` sparingly

## Accessibility Standards (WCAG AA)
- Color contrast ratio: 4.5:1 minimum
- Focus indicators: 2-3px outline with accent color
- Keyboard navigation: Tab, Enter, Space, Arrow keys
- Screen reader compatibility
- Semantic HTML structure

## Reduced Motion Support
```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  * {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
}
```

## JavaScript Performance
- Bundle size: < 10 KB min+gz
- No external dependencies
- Debounce scroll events
- Cleanup event listeners
- Graceful degradation

## Image Optimization
- Inline SVG only (no raster images)
- Optimize SVG code
- Use CSS gradients for backgrounds
- No external image requests

## Core Web Vitals
- Optimize for LCP (Largest Contentful Paint)
- Minimize CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift)
- Improve FID (First Input Delay)
- Use proper loading strategies

## Browser Support
- Latest Chrome, Safari, Firefox
- Graceful degradation for older browsers
- Feature detection for modern APIs
- Fallbacks for unsupported features

## Testing Requirements
- Cross-browser testing
- Lighthouse audits
- Accessibility testing with screen readers
- Performance monitoring
- Mobile responsiveness testing
